# KC live bench transcripts land here.
#
# Run scripts/run-kc-live.sh (Linux/macOS) or scripts/run-kc-live.ps1 (Windows) with
# RUN_LIVE_LLM=1 + the LLM API keys exported; the script copies
# TestResults/kc_live_summary.md + run-*.json + kc_metrics_live.csv into a
# timestamped subdirectory beneath this folder.
#
# Subdirectory naming: {mode}-{utc-timestamp}/  (e.g. hybrid-20260601T093015Z/).
